{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01Dn1C7HukkpdGYVjHAmmjn2","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Here are the full contents of both files:\n\n## 1. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/backend/services/backend/migrations/011_challenge_engine.sql`\n\n**`completion_bonuses` table schema (lines 114-124):**\n```sql\nCREATE TABLE completion_bonuses (\n  id              BIGINT GENERATED ALWAYS AS IDENTITY PRIMARY KEY,\n  campaign_id     BIGINT NOT NULL REFERENCES campaigns(id),\n  title           TEXT NOT NULL,\n  description     TEXT,\n  required_count  INT NOT NULL,\n  reward_type     TEXT NOT NULL CHECK (reward_type IN ('points', 'crate')),\n  reward_amount   INT,\n  is_active       BOOLEAN NOT NULL DEFAULT true,\n  created_at      TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT now()\n);\n```\n\n**`bonus_completions` table schema (lines 127-134):**\n```sql\nCREATE TABLE bonus_completions (\n  id              BIGINT GENERATED ALWAYS AS IDENTITY PRIMARY KEY,\n  user_id         TEXT NOT NULL,\n  bonus_id        BIGINT NOT NULL REFERENCES completion_bonuses(id),\n  period_key      TEXT NOT NULL,\n  completed_at    TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT now(),\n  UNIQUE (user_id, bonus_id, period_key)\n);\n```\n\n**Seed data for completion bonuses (lines 236-238):**\n```sql\nINSERT INTO completion_bonuses (campaign_id, title, description, required_count, reward_type) VALUES\n  ((SELECT id FROM campaigns WHERE name = 'Daily Challenges'), 'Daily Bonus Crate', 'Complete all daily challenges for a bonus crate', 3, 'crate');\n```\n\n---\n\n## 2. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/backend/services/backend/src/queue/handlers/reward-pool-fund.ts`\n\n**`readRewardConfig` export pattern (lines 16-25):**\n```typescript\nexport async function readRewardConfig(\n  db: Db,\n  key: string,\n): Promise<string | null> {\n  const rows = await db.rawSql<{ value: string }[]>`\n    SELECT value FROM reward_config WHERE key = ${key}\n  `;\n  return rows.length > 0 ? rows[0]!.value : null;\n}\n```\n\nThe function is exported directly as a named export at module level. It accepts a `Db` instance and a config key string, executes a raw SQL query to fetch the config value from the `reward_config` table, and returns the value as a string or null if not found."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"6576ed6a-06e5-40ef-875a-a4c0ef7a496b","uuid":"53274872-2130-4bdf-a122-b64155b0cf16","timestamp":"2026-04-03T20:20:03.070Z","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Read and report the full contents of:\n1. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/backend/services/backend/migrations/011_challenge_engine.sql` — I need the `completion_bonuses` and `bonus_completions` table schemas, as well as the seed data for completion bonuses\n2. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/backend/services/backend/src/queue/handlers/reward-pool-fund.ts` — I need to see the `readRewardConfig` export pattern\n\nReport the full contents of both files.","agentId":"a33772875bafb7995","agentType":"Explore","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Here are the full contents of both files:\n\n## 1. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/backend/services/backend/migrations/011_challenge_engine.sql`\n\n**`completion_bonuses` table schema (lines 114-124):**\n```sql\nCREATE TABLE completion_bonuses (\n  id              BIGINT GENERATED ALWAYS AS IDENTITY PRIMARY KEY,\n  campaign_id     BIGINT NOT NULL REFERENCES campaigns(id),\n  title           TEXT NOT NULL,\n  description     TEXT,\n  required_count  INT NOT NULL,\n  reward_type     TEXT NOT NULL CHECK (reward_type IN ('points', 'crate')),\n  reward_amount   INT,\n  is_active       BOOLEAN NOT NULL DEFAULT true,\n  created_at      TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT now()\n);\n```\n\n**`bonus_completions` table schema (lines 127-134):**\n```sql\nCREATE TABLE bonus_completions (\n  id              BIGINT GENERATED ALWAYS AS IDENTITY PRIMARY KEY,\n  user_id         TEXT NOT NULL,\n  bonus_id        BIGINT NOT NULL REFERENCES completion_bonuses(id),\n  period_key      TEXT NOT NULL,\n  completed_at    TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT now(),\n  UNIQUE (user_id, bonus_id, period_key)\n);\n```\n\n**Seed data for completion bonuses (lines 236-238):**\n```sql\nINSERT INTO completion_bonuses (campaign_id, title, description, required_count, reward_type) VALUES\n  ((SELECT id FROM campaigns WHERE name = 'Daily Challenges'), 'Daily Bonus Crate', 'Complete all daily challenges for a bonus crate', 3, 'crate');\n```\n\n---\n\n## 2. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/backend/services/backend/src/queue/handlers/reward-pool-fund.ts`\n\n**`readRewardConfig` export pattern (lines 16-25):**\n```typescript\nexport async function readRewardConfig(\n  db: Db,\n  key: string,\n): Promise<string | null> {\n  const rows = await db.rawSql<{ value: string }[]>`\n    SELECT value FROM reward_config WHERE key = ${key}\n  `;\n  return rows.length > 0 ? rows[0]!.value : null;\n}\n```\n\nThe function is exported directly as a named export at module level. It accepts a `Db` instance and a config key string, executes a raw SQL query to fetch the config value from the `reward_config` table, and returns the value as a string or null if not found."}],"totalDurationMs":7078,"totalTokens":36962,"totalToolUseCount":2,"usage":{"input_tokens":1490,"cache_creation_input_tokens":8040,"cache_read_input_tokens":26810,"output_tokens":622,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":8040},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
