{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01K3HHnXZYzfSc9sUzLpNNpp","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Now I have the complete file. Let me provide you with a comprehensive report:\n\n## Full Integration Test File Report\n\n**File:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/backend/services/backend/src/__tests__/integration.test.ts`\n\n---\n\n### IMPORTS AND SETUP\n\n**Imports:**\n- Testing: `vitest` (describe, it, beforeAll, afterAll, beforeEach, expect)\n- Solana: `@solana/web3.js` (Keypair, PublicKey, SystemProgram, LAMPORTS_PER_SOL, Connection)\n- Database: `postgres`\n- JWT: `jose` (SignJWT) with HS256 algorithm\n- Application modules:\n  - `createDb` from `db.js`\n  - `createCoinflipRoutes` from `routes/create.js`\n  - `createRoundsRoutes` from `routes/rounds.js`\n  - `createJwtAuthMiddleware` from `middleware/jwt-auth.js`\n  - Settlement workers: `createSettlementWorker`, `settleMatch` from `worker/settlement.js` and `worker/settle-tx.js`\n  - `createRetrySettler` from `worker/retry.js`\n  - Account decoders: `encodeCoinflipMatch`, `encodeCoinflipConfig`, `encodeCloseCallRound` from `worker/account-decoder.js`\n  - Close Call clock worker: `createCloseCallClockWorker` from `worker/closecall-clock.js`\n  - Queue handlers: `createRewardPoolFundHandler`, `createPointsGrantHandler`, `createCrateDropHandler`, `createGameSettledHandler` from `queue/handlers/*`\n  - Configuration: Various fairness and platform config modules\n\n**Constants:**\n- `DATABASE_URL` = PostgreSQL connection (defaults to localhost)\n- `AMOUNT_LAMPORTS` = 5,000,000\n- `SIDE_HEADS` = 0\n- `PHASE_LOCKED` = 1\n- `JWT_SECRET` = \"test-secret-for-integration-tests\" (HS256)\n\n**JWT Helper Functions:**\n- `makeJwt(wallet, userId)` — creates HS256 JWT with subject, issued_at, expiration (1 hour)\n- `userIdFromWallet(wallet)` — derives user_id from wallet address (format: `usr_{first_8_chars}`)\n\n---\n\n### MOCK CONNECTION CLASS\n\nCustom `MockConnection` implementation:\n- In-memory account storage (Map<pubkey, account_data>)\n- Methods: `setAccount()`, `removeAccount()`, `getLatestBlockhash()`, `getSlot()`, `getAccountInfo()`, `getProgramAccounts()` (with filter support), `sendRawTransaction()`, `confirmTransaction()`, `getBlockTime()`, `getBalance()`\n- Mutable slot tracking for settlement readiness testing\n- Stores last raw transaction (for inspection)\n\n---\n\n### ACCOUNT DATA BUILDERS\n\n- `buildMatchAccountData()` — encodes CoinFlip match state (using `encodeCoinflipMatch`)\n- `buildConfigAccountData()` — encodes CoinFlip config account\n- `buildPlatformConfigData()` — builds 74-byte PlatformConfig buffer with authority (offset 8), treasury (offset 40), fee_bps u16LE (offset 72)\n\n---\n\n### SETUP AND TEARDOWN\n\n**beforeAll:**\n- Creates PostgreSQL raw connection\n- **TRUNCATE list** (from line 401):\n  ```\n  rounds, closecall_rounds, closecall_candles, operator_events, event_queue, \n  game_entries, transactions, player_profiles, referral_codes, referral_links, \n  referral_earnings, referral_claims, referral_kol_rates, reward_pool_fundings, \n  point_grants, player_points, dogpile_events, crate_drops, progress_events, \n  challenge_assignments, bonus_completions\n  ```\n- Creates referral tables if not present (codes, links, earnings, claims, KOL rates)\n- Creates the typed `Db` instance with `createDb(DATABASE_URL, rawSql)`\n\n**afterAll:**\n- Closes db and rawSql connections\n\n**beforeEach:**\n- **TRUNCATE all tables with RESTART IDENTITY CASCADE** (comprehensive cleanup for isolation)\n- Resets reward_pool to zero balance (keeps singleton row from migration)\n- Clears PlatformConfig cache via `resetPlatformConfigCache()`\n- Creates fresh `MockConnection`\n- Pre-populates mock with:\n  - Entropy account (32-byte buffer with test data)\n  - CoinFlip config PDA (derived from [\"coinflip_config\"])\n  - PlatformConfig PDA (derived from platform config) with fee_bps=500 (5%)\n- Builds Hono app with:\n  - JWT auth middleware on `/coinflip/*`\n  - CoinFlip routes\n  - Rounds routes\n\n---\n\n### TEST PATTERNS\n\n#### **Full Lifecycle Tests (Coinflip)**\nPattern: Create → Mock Join (LOCKED state) → Settle → Verify\n\nExample: `\"full lifecycle: create → join (mock) → settle → verify\"`\n1. POST `/coinflip/create` → returns transaction, matchPda, commitment, matchId\n2. Verify DB round is in \"created\" phase with secret, commitment, operator_events\n3. Simulate on-chain join by setting match account to PHASE_LOCKED in mock\n4. Create settlement worker + retry settler\n5. Call `worker.poll()` (single cycle) + await settlement promise\n6. Verify DB round moved to \"settled\" phase with result_hash, result_side, winner\n7. Verify operator_events trail (secret_generated, match_detected, settle_submitted, settle_confirmed)\n8. GET `/rounds/:pda` → verify response includes secret (32-byte hex), verification object\n\n#### **Referral Earnings Tests**\n- Setup referral code + link (referrer → opponent is referee)\n- Create → Join → Settle\n- Verify `referral_earnings` row with correct calculations:\n  - `fee = wager * fee_bps / 10000`\n  - `referrer_earned = fee * referrer_rate_bps / 10000`\n  - `referee_rebate = fee * referee_rebate_rate_bps / 10000` (fixed 10%)\n- KOL test: Custom rate_bps from `referral_kol_rates` overrides default\n\n#### **Game.Settled Event Tests**\n- Settle directly (after transitioning round to \"locked\" phase)\n- Verify `event_queue` row with event_type=\"game.settled\"\n- Payload shape:\n  ```json\n  {\n    roundId, roundPda, game, feeLamports, settledAt,\n    players: [\n      { userId, wallet, amountLamports, isWinner, payoutLamports, isCreator }\n    ]\n  }\n  ```\n- Close Call: Same structure but with minuteTs as roundId, green/red players, outcome logic\n\n#### **Reward Queue Handler Tests**\n\n**reward.pool_fund:**\n- Takes feeLamports, computes funded = floor(feeLamports * fee_share)\n- Upserts `reward_pool_fundings` row (dedupes on round_id)\n- Increments `reward_pool.balance_lamports` and `lifetime_funded`\n\n**points.grant:**\n- Calculates points = floor(lamports_to_usd * points_per_dollar * multiplier)\n- Dedupes on user_id + source_type + source_id\n- Upsets `player_points` (balance + lifetime_earned)\n- Supports multiplier from dogpile events (2.0x when active)\n- Handles \"crate_points\" source type (pre-calculated amount)\n\n**crate.drop:**\n- RNG roll determines crate type: SOL (< 0.01), Points (< 0.06), Miss\n- SOL crate: floor(pool * 0.10), must be >= 10M lamports; emits crate.sol_payout\n- Points crate: 500–5000 points (randomized); emits points.grant\n- Dedupes on user_id + trigger_id\n\n**game.settled handler:**\n- Iterates players, processes challenge progress\n- Matches on challenge.condition (game_completed, game_won) and scope\n- Increments `challenge_assignments.progress` once per game\n- On completion: emits points.grant with source_type=\"challenge_completed\"\n- Emits reward.pool_fund, points.grant (wager), crate.drop per player\n- Skips refunded games (isWinner === null)\n- Dedupes on round_id + user_id (via progress_events)\n\n---\n\n### KEY PATTERNS SUMMARY\n\n1. **Assignment Creation:** Manually inserted via `INSERT INTO challenge_assignments (user_id, challenge_id, period_key, target) VALUES (...)`\n2. **Deduplication:** Each handler checks for existing rows by domain key (round_id, user_id, source_id) before mutating\n3. **Event Emission:** Handlers enqueue events to `event_queue` (event_type, payload JSON, status='pending')\n4. **Isolation:** Full TRUNCATE + table reset ensures test independence\n5. **Referral Model:** Separate tables for codes, links, earnings, KOL rates; referrer_rate_bps overridable per user\n6. **Settlement:** Coordinator worker discovers locked matches, calls `settleMatch()` with entropy + server key, records operator audit trail"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"6576ed6a-06e5-40ef-875a-a4c0ef7a496b","uuid":"39e6af5a-98fb-4bcd-bcca-cda1528